commit 46773df61c984813aece7d06e9a9fe5cc27476a9
Author: David Zeuthen <davidz@redhat.com>
Date:   Tue Jul 24 13:29:33 2007 -0400

    document the /etc/PolicyKit/PolicyKit.conf file with a manual page

